<li><a href=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/Programme_MI_AR.pdf\">Nouveau programme Licence en arabe 1er ann\u00e9e MI Juillet 2013<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-very-light-gray-to-cyan-bluish-gray-gradient-background has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-elements-40fec88f9c8184b34805b07f8f95f54d is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"color:#000000;padding-top:2em;padding-right:2em;padding-bottom:2em;padding-left:2em\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"single\" style=\"font-size:40px\"><strong>Licence<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\" style=\"line-height:1.5\"><strong><strong>La facult\u00e9 d&#8217;Informatique dispense actuellement 4 licences<\/strong><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-css-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#000000;color:#000000\"\/>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-normal-font-size wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/licence-informatique\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"219\">Licence Informatique (LI)<\/a>  <br> Responsable : Dr. BESSAA Brahim<\/li><li><a href=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/licence-gtr\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"223\">Licence G\u00e9nie des T\u00e9l\u00e9communications et R\u00e9seaux (GTR)<\/a> <br> Responsable : Dr. ZAFFOUNE Youcef<\/li><li><a href=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/licence-isil\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"221\">Licence Ing\u00e9nierie des Syst\u00e8mes d&#8217;Information et des Logiciels (ISIL)<\/a><br> Responsable : Dr. SEDDIKI Manel<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/systemes-dinformation-et-genie-logiciel\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"4606\">Licence Syst\u00e8mes d\u2019Information et G\u00e9nie Logiciel (SIGL)<\/a> <strong>(A DISTANCE)<\/strong><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Les parcours de licence comprennent chacun trois ann\u00e9es de formation (L1, L2 et L3), le L1 \u00e9tant un tronc commun du domaine MI (Math\u00e9matiques et informatique). les \u00e9tudiants sont orient\u00e9s du L1 vers L2, selon leur classement et leur fiche de v\u0153ux, en tenant compte de la disponibilit\u00e9 des places p\u00e9dagogiques au d\u00e9partement. En fin de cursus (semestre S6) les \u00e9tudiants en licence pr\u00e9parent un projet de fin d&#8217;\u00e9tudes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons alignfull is-horizontal is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-2 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-very-light-gray-to-cyan-bluish-gray-gradient-background has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-elements-42dd780455cc6bf7b377e3308dfa7f62 is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"color:#000000;padding-top:2em;padding-right:2em;padding-bottom:2em;padding-left:2em\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"single\" style=\"font-size:40px\"><strong>Master<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\" style=\"line-height:1.5\"><strong><strong>La formation est \u00e9tal\u00e9e sur 04 semestres, le dernier semestre est consacr\u00e9 \u00e0 un projet.<\/strong><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-css-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#000000;color:#000000\"\/>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"has-normal-font-size wp-block-list\"><li> <a href=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/master-reseaux-et-systemes-distribues\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"235\">Master R\u00e9seaux et Syst\u00e8mes Distribu\u00e9s (RSD)<\/a> <br>  Responsable : Dr. ZERAOULIA Khaled <\/li><li> <a href=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/master-ingenierie-de-logiciels\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"239\">Master Ing\u00e9nierie de Logiciels (IL)<\/a>  <br>  Responsable : Dr. KHEMISSA Hamid <\/li><li> <a href=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/master-systemes-informatiques-intelligents\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"241\">Master Syst\u00e8mes Informatiques Intelligents (SII)<\/a> <br> Responsable : Pr. AZZOUNE Hamid <\/li><li> <a href=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/master-securite-des-systemes-informatiques\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"243\">Master S\u00e9curit\u00e9 des Syst\u00e8mes Informatiques (SSI)<\/a> <br> Responsable : Dr. GUERROUMI Mohamed <\/li><li> <a href=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/master-bigdata\/\" data-type=\"page\">Master 2 BIGDATA Analytics (BIGDATAA) <\/a> <br> Responsable : Pr. ALIMAZIGHI Zaia <\/li><li> <a href=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/master-mathematiques-et-informatique-decisionnelle-mind\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"925\">Master 1 Math\u00e9matique et Informatique D\u00e9cisionnelle (MIND)<\/a><br>  Responsable : Pr. BOUKHALFA Kamel <\/li><li> <a href=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/master-informatique-visuelle\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"253\">Master Informatique Visuelle (IV)<\/a>  <br>  Responsable : Dr. DAHMANE Afifa <\/li><li> <a href=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/master-bio-informatique\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"249\">Master Bio Informatique (BIOINFO)<\/a> <br> Responsable : Dr. BOUKHEDOUMA Saida<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/master-calcul-haute-performance\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"2758\">Master Calcul Haute Performance (HPC)<\/a><br> Responsable :Dr. BABA ALI Riadh<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons alignfull is-horizontal is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-3 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide 